cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.DC 

The paper discusses the design challenges for the dense heterogeneous Cloud-RAN based on convex optimization, which involves optimization of wireless networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), as the paper discusses the use of cloud data centers and parallel implementation for solving large-scale convex optimization problems.
